flowchart TD
    %% CPU 训练
    A[命令: sanguo] --> B[Program.TrainSanguo]
    B --> C[GetSanguoDataPaths<br/>解析 data 或 Data 目录]
    C --> D[SanguoQaDataLoader.Load<br/>ReadJsonl + 构建 CharVocabulary]
    D --> E[构造 TransformerModel<br/>dModel=64, numHeads=2, ...]
    E --> F[epoch 循环]
    F --> G[DataGenerator.BatchesTokenized<br/>添加 SOS/EOS/PAD]
    G --> H[Training.TrainEpochBackpropTokenized]
    H --> I[Training.ValidateTokenized]
    I --> F
    F --> J[保存模型与词表<br/>输出目录 SanguoModel]
    J --> K[TransformerModel.SaveToDirectory]
    J --> L[CharVocabulary.SaveToDirectory]

    %% GPU 训练
    A2[命令: sanguo gpu] --> B2[Program.TrainSanguoGpu]
    B2 --> C2[GetSanguoDataPaths]
    C2 --> D2[SanguoQaDataLoader.Load]
    D2 --> E2[SanguoGpuTrainer.TrainOnGpu]
    E2 --> F2[DataGenerator.BatchesTokenized<br/>在 GPU 上循环训练]
    F2 --> G2[验证 loss 输出]
    G2 --> H2[ExportToCSharpFormat<br/>映射权重到 C# 模型]
    H2 --> I2[TransformerModel.SaveToDirectory]
    H2 --> J2[CharVocabulary.SaveToDirectory]
